# Stray debug/lock artifacts from git operations on this session's mount --
# see PROGRESS_LOG Session 6 "workspace mount doesn't support unlink()" note.
# rm/unlink fails here (Operation not permitted) even for files this same
# session created, so leftovers from lock-rollback and other git-internal
# unlink calls sometimes can't be cleaned up and are ignored instead.
*.lock.stale.*
/ovr_a.txt
/retry_unlink.tmp
/test_unlink_check.tmp

# Scheduled-task scratch files: drive the autonomous research-assistant
# session locally, not part of the project's code/deliverables.
/project_overview.md
/PROGRESS_LOG.md
/NEEDS_YOUR_INPUT.md

# GitHub push credential for the scheduled task (contains a token; must
# never be committed).
/.credentials/
